# SprintCycle baseline (代理基线)

## One workflow entry (唯一工作流入口)

**`/sprint`** — modes: `sdd` · `optimize` · `evolve` · `commit`  
Canonical index: `.cursor/README.md`

| Mode | When |
|------|------|
| **sdd** (default for substantive work) | Scope, L/F grade, PRD/plan, principle review |
| **optimize** | Medium+ refactors, DDD cleanup, field alignment |
| **evolve** | Semi-automated detection → optimize |
| **commit** | Draft commit message (`it-commit-message-agent`) |

**CI repair (separate)**: `/ci-fix-loop` — not `/sprint`.

## Governance docs (治理文档)

- Constitution: `docs/SPRINTCYCLE_CONSTITUTION.md`
- SDD gates: `docs/SPRINT_SDD_GATES.md`
- Optimize phases: `docs/SPRINT_OPTIMIZE_WORKFLOW.md`
- Architecture (slim): `sprintcycle-architecture-orchestration.mdc` · (full) `docs/CURSOR_ARCHITECTURE_ORCHESTRATION.md`

## Artifacts (落档)

`docs/sdd-designs/YYYY-MM-DD/` · template: `docs/templates/sdd-feature-template.md`  
Archive: `docs/archive/specs/` (read-only)

## Before substantive coding (编码前)

Grade L/F (`sprintcycle-workflow.mdc`); L2+/F1+ need dated docs; HITL before implement.
